'''阿貝迪勒利'''（{{lang-en|Abertillery}}）是位於[[英國|英國]][[威爾斯|威爾斯]]南部[[布萊耐格溫特|布萊耐格溫特]]的一座城鎮。據2001年英國[[人口普查|人口普查]]，阿貝迪勒利有人1,146人會講威爾斯語，佔總人口的9.9%<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.byig-wlb.org.uk/English/publications/Pages/PublicationItem.aspx?puburl=/English%2fpublications%2fPublications%2f786.xls |title=No. & Percentage Welsh speakers 3+ By Community and Age |author=The Welsh Language Board |date=26 February 2004 |format=[[Microsoft_Excel#File_formats|XLS]] |postscript=<!--None--> |access-date=2022-02-13 |archive-date=2011-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524061946/http://www.byig-wlb.org.uk/English/publications/Pages/PublicationItem.aspx?puburl=%2FEnglish%2Fpublications%2FPublications%2F786.xls |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。不過在2011年人口普查時，這一數字降到7.2%<ref>[http://www.comisiynyddygymraeg.org/Cymraeg/Cymorth/dataacystadegau/Pages/Cyfrifiad2011canlyniadauynolCymuned.aspx Comisiynydd y Gymraeg - Cyfrifiad 2011: canlyniadau yn ôl Cymuned. Retrieved 7 June 2014] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150106040653/http://www.comisiynyddygymraeg.org/Cymraeg/Cymorth/dataacystadegau/Pages/Cyfrifiad2011canlyniadauynolCymuned.aspx |date=6 一月 2015 }}</ref>。

